messages.messageBody:
-----Original Message-----
From: tibetandesertdragon <licia@...>


Hey there Kelly...I can't find the post about rv parking at the
hotel...would you repost the message? Thank you for any help!

-=-=-=-=-


This was posted by Heidi at the LiveandLearnConference yahoogroup:

"I just called the hotel about the possibility of parking motorhomes at
the hotel and she said absolutely no problem! I guess they have a lot
of NASCAR people that stay there and bring their big semis. She said
just please park at the far end of the parking lot. I asked her if it
would be a problem if there were several motorhomes and she said that
would be fine. She is also finding out what the closest RV park is to
the hotel and she will be calling me back on that just in case there
are some who want that, very helpful! "


Kelly Lovejoy
Conference Coordinator

October 6-9, 2005

messages.subject: conference registration deadline
messages.msgSnippet: I just want to remind everyone that the conference s Early Bird Deadline is THIS Sunday, July 31. Postmarked by that date is fine---don t bust a gut to try to
messages.messageBody:
I just want to remind everyone that the conference's Early Bird
Deadline is THIS Sunday, July 31.

Postmarked by that date is fine---don't bust a gut to try to get it
here *before* then.

Funshop presenters also need to fill out registrations! Just because
you're working doesn't mean you don't wear a nametag! Please get
registrations to me.

If you have decided not to come and have an already reserved hotel room
you will not be using, please announce it on the
LiveandLearnConference@yahoogroups.com e-list. I know someone will be
willing to take it!

And isn't it cool about the RV parking at the hotel? <g>

Thanks so much!

~Kelly


Kelly Lovejoy
Conference Coordinator
Live and Learn Unschooling Conference
October 6-9, 2005
http://liveandlearnconference.org
